    "description": "Due to some unforeseen circumstances, you have lost your kid whose name is Milo to some bigger authority which has more power but now you have to take the revenge and go on the journey to find your kid in this cruel world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/11a7a16f7ccd21d6e18eee400e3bf180.poster.avif?t=1718962775\" width=440 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/11a7a16f7ccd21d6e18eee400e3bf180.webm?t=1718962775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/11a7a16f7ccd21d6e18eee400e3bf180.mp4?t=1718962775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A Lost Whisker is a Third Person Cat adventure game with some action on your journey where you play as a Cat named Meimei. The game portrays a stunning environment and a cozy Japanese setting. Meet new friends in your journey to find your kid and save others from some cruel beings, as you progress you will face difficult obstacles, puzzles, and foes who will try to stop you from getting together with your kid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/e9d57cc368b04488c9441d6b2b06144f.poster.avif?t=1718962775\" width=440 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/e9d57cc368b04488c9441d6b2b06144f.webm?t=1718962775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/e9d57cc368b04488c9441d6b2b06144f.mp4?t=1718962775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>See the world through the eyes of a cat and interact with the environment in playful ways. Be stealthy, nimble, silly, and sometimes have fun with fellow animals in the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/a40e1c206603d5d162e17274f9c01c4c.poster.avif?t=1718962775\" width=440 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/a40e1c206603d5d162e17274f9c01c4c.webm?t=1718962775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051260/extras/a40e1c206603d5d162e17274f9c01c4c.mp4?t=1718962775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A Lost Whisker is developed by Crazy Paws Games, who is a Solo Developer following his passion for games.",
